data.description: Plenty of room for your horses, cattle, FFA animals and projects. Wow, this desirable location off Williams Ranch Road (FM 2525), has large trees, almost 15 acres, wet weather creek, running shute, 12X12 horse stall, perm wash rack, 5 pens, 2 small bays. Escape to the back of this property and you are in a hunter's dream with deer, dove and turkey. Bring ideas to create an outdoor living space, as views off of the back of the patio will make you feel far away from town. Two car garage with remote, detached carport, space for RV, boat, and horse trailer. 4B,2B (2nd B is walk-in shower), open floor plan with cozy fireplace to be enjoyed while in the kitchen, living, and dining room. Range and overhead microwave are WIFI controlled. Stainless steel refrigerator will convey. Walk-in pantry. Possible income with excellent road frontage for RV spots. Build a hunting cabin, or build your dream home and rent the front property as an airbnb. Ag appraised. No homestead exemption currently.
